    "en": "Folic Acid Injection is a yellow to orange-yel-low, clear liquid. MS: Amount (mg) of p-Aminobenzoyl Glutamic Acid for Purity RS taken MT: Amount (mg) of Folic Acid taken, calculated on the anhydrous basis pH: 8.0 – 11.0"
